# Helix Ultimate Core

Two components, one framework:

| Component | Path | Role |
|-----------|------|------|
| System plugin | `plugins/system/helixultimate/` | Framework logic, AJAX, fields, overrides |
| Template | `templates/shaper_helixultimate/` | Frontend consumer (features, SCSS, `html/`) |

Before architectural changes, read `AGENTS.md` and `SOUL.md`.

## Hard rules

- Never edit Joomla core (`components/`, `modules/`, `libraries/`). Use overrides.
- Prefer `HelixUltimate\Framework\Platform\Helper` over reinventing utilities.
- Joomla 4+: namespaced CMS APIs (`Joomla\CMS\Factory`). No `JFactory`.
- New styles → SCSS. New scripts → Vanilla JS (ES6). No new jQuery.
- Bootstrap 5 utilities for layout before custom CSS.

## Boot chain

```
templates/shaper_helixultimate/index.php
  → require plugins/system/helixultimate/bootstrap.php
  → new HelixUltimate\Framework\Core\HelixUltimate
```

PSR-4: `HelixUltimate\Framework\` → `plugins/system/helixultimate/src/`

## Where to put work

- Framework / AJAX / fields → plugin `src/`
- Site look & features → template `features/`, `scss/`, `js/`
- View changes → `templates/shaper_helixultimate/html/` (or plugin `overrides/` for all Helix sites)
